    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hand or rifle grenades containing a smoke-producing chemical mixture, used for signaling or screening. Different types produce either white or colored smoke.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
